Notes
Large files: Useful for identifying media, backups, or unused installers.

Duplicate detection: Hash-based comparison ensures accuracy but may be slower.

Temporary files: Safe to delete, but the utility recommends reviewing duplicates and large files manually.

Dry-run mode: Prevents accidental deletion by showing what would be removed before execution.

Reports: Saved in disk_cleanup_report.json for later review.
